        <a href="http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2014/03/bank-that-claimed-to-solve-bitcoins-security-problem-robbed-shuts-down/?comments=1&amp;post=26360099#comment-26360099" class="timeago datetime">jump to post</a>
        
          
        
